### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

### Get a single contact by ID (replace YOUR_CONTACT_ID with an actual ID from your database)
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/YOUR_CONTACT_ID

### Test the deployed Render URL (replace with your actual Render URL)
GET https://your-app-name.onrender.com/contacts

### Get single contact from Render
GET https://your-app-name.onrender.com/contacts/YOUR_CONTACT_ID